dct_description_sm: Variant title: Indiana 1:25,000. Filing title: Marietta, Indiana. Printed with vegetation. Standard map series designation: Series V851 Sheet 3862 IV NW. Edition 3-DMATC. Transverse Mercator projection. "12-75 printed by defense mapping agency topographic center." "Copied in 1975 from Indiana 1:24,000, U. S. G. S., Marietta, 1962. Scale change and marginal data revised, 1975." "Stock no. V851X38624NW." "D.M.A. Series V851" Issued in 7 1/2 minute quadrangles. "Transverse Mercator projection." "Contour interval 10 feet." Marginal maps: Index to boundaries.--Index to adjoining sheets.
Imprint: Washington, D.C. : Defense Mapping Agency Topographic Center, 1975.
Dimensions: 56 x 45 cm or smaller; Scale: 1:25,000
dct_publisher_sm: United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Topographic Center
